dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Adam Scott. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Angela. Can you provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five eight two four six, and my date of birth is zero five two eight one nine eight seven.
Thank you, Angela. I also need your current address to update our records. Please provide your street address including the city and zip code.
Of course, my address is two one four Cedar Street, Forest City, three one five four zero.
Thank you, Angela, for providing the information. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Angela. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day.
